# Campus Confessions Feature

Anonymous discussion feed where students can post, like, comment on, and report confessions. User identity is hidden publicly but stored internally for moderation.

## Proposed Changes

---

### Backend — Models

#### [NEW] `Confession.ts`
```ts
{ userId, text, createdAt, likesCount, reportCount, isDeleted, isHidden }
```
- `userId` — stored for moderation, never exposed to clients
- `isDeleted` — soft delete by admins
- `isHidden` — hidden after too many reports

#### [NEW] `ConfessionComment.ts`
```ts
{ confessionId, userId, text, createdAt }
```

#### [NEW] `ConfessionReaction.ts`
```ts
{ confessionId, userId, type: 'like' | 'report' }
```
One reaction per user per confession (unique compound index).

---

### Backend — Routes & Controllers

#### [NEW] `confessionRoutes.ts` → `/api/confessions`

| Method | Route | Action |
|--------|-------|--------|
| GET | `/` | Get paginated confessions (sort: newest/top) |
| POST | `/` | Post a new confession |
| POST | `/:id/like` | Toggle like |
| POST | `/:id/report` | Report confession |
| GET | `/:id/comments` | Get comments |
| POST | `/:id/comments` | Add a comment |
| DELETE | `/:id` | Admin only — delete confession |
| POST | `/:id/ban` | Admin only — ban the user who posted |

#### [MODIFY] `server.ts`
Add `confessionRoutes` import and mount at `/api/confessions`.

