### Admin Moderation

- `user.role === 'admin'` check (already in User model assumed)
- Admin sees **Delete** button on each ConfessionCard
- Admin sees **Ban User** option on reported confessions (calls `/api/confessions/:id/ban`)
- Ban sets `user.isBanned = true` in MongoDB

